{"tid":1476344,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠首度為反送中表態: 黃台之瓜，何堪再摘","createTime":"2019-08-15T19:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T22:45:48.000Z","uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"741d4f2bac751997bac96407839040c8a27bf755","tid":1476344,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:18:16.000Z","msg":"在歷時多月的反送中修例運動中，取態偏低調的本地華資地產商，周中紛紛表態公開跟隨「止暴制亂」主調，四大地產商及後亦再個別於報章刊登聲明，呼籲盡快恢復社會秩序。而一直從未表態的本港首富李嘉誠，今日在多份報章以個人名義「發言」八個字：「黃台之瓜，何堪再摘。」，署名為一個香港市民李嘉誠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRAp3nm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRAp3nm.jpg&h=58b4026d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b4c3721767ab0c06f168b9297e6fd995d209cf7","tid":1476344,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTBpiWi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTBpiWi.gif&h=aa1d9fa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ef9b4dffc2e917749996ec2ad6456cf26c296b5","tid":1476344,"uid":202622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:20:03.000Z","msg":"即係？中文唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d434d04a42bb713e2e0b0a0123a6295ea603c9","tid":1476344,"uid":54228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ef9b4dffc2e917749996ec2ad6456cf26c296b5","tid":1476344,"uid":202622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:20:03.000Z","msg":"即係？中文唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:21:06.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠：黃台之瓜，何堪再摘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476309</a><br />\n<br />\n入面有解釋"},{"pid":"e65d44821341100c481ac6d83b5e971036a579ef","tid":1476344,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ef9b4dffc2e917749996ec2ad6456cf26c296b5","tid":1476344,"uid":202622,"lik